{
  "title": "Prometheus — обзорные метрики",
  "uid": "siem-prometheus-stats",
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "time": { "from": "now-24h", "to": "now" },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "tags": ["prometheus", "monitoring", "siem"],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "ℹ️ О дашборде Prometheus",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 3 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Prometheus Server — мониторинг системы сбора метрик\n\nЭтот дашборд показывает **здоровье самого Prometheus** (не SIEM события!):\n\n**Панели:**\n- **Targets ready** — количество scrape целей\n- **Scrape failures** — ошибки сбора метрик (должно быть 0)\n- **WAL коррупции** — проблемы базы данных (должно быть 0)\n- **Prometheus UP** — статус сервера\n\n**Если графики пустые:**\n- Prometheus ещё не запустился — подождите 60 секунд\n- Проверьте: `docker ps | grep prometheus`\n- Метрики появятся после первого scrape цикла (15 сек)\n\n**Настройка:** `deploy/docker/prometheus.yml`"
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Targets ready",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 3, "w": 8, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "prometheus_target_scrape_pool_targets{job=\"prometheus\"} or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "pool targets" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "hidden" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Scrape failures",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 8, "y": 3, "w": 8, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "rate(prometheus_target_scrapes_failed_total{job=\"prometheus\"}[5m]) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "failed/s" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "cps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "hidden" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "WAL коррупции / проблемы",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 16, "y": 3, "w": 8, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "rate(prometheus_tsdb_wal_corruptions_total{job=\"prometheus\"}[1h]) or vector(0)", "legendFormat": "corruptions/s" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "cps", "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 } } },
      "options": { "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }, "legend": { "displayMode": "hidden" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Prometheus UP",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 11, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-siem" },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "up{job=\"prometheus\"} or vector(0)", "instant": true }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [{ "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "DOWN", "color": "red" }, "1": { "text": "UP", "color": "green" } } }],
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "red", "value": null }, { "color": "green", "value": 1 }] }
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none" }
    }
  ]
}
